(53, 1, '2013-02-20 09:47:13', '2013-02-20 09:47:13', '<div class="features-big">\n<div class="container features-content">\n\n<a href="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature01.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2217" alt="Feature01" src="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature01.jpg" width="950" height="420" /></a>\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">The ultimate multi purpose eCommerce Wordpress theme.</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">BearStore is a clean, responsive &amp; retina-ready eCommerce WordPress theme.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Built for <span style="color: red;">WooCommerce 2.0+</span>, it includes everything you need to start selling today!</p>\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="features-big">\n<div class="container features-content">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Easy and Elegan.</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Managing your products has never been easier or looked better.</p>\n<a href="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature02.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2221" alt="Feature02" src="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature02.jpg" width="950" height="700" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature03.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2222" alt="Feature03" src="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature03.jpg" width="950" height="600" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="features-big">\n<div class="container features-content">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Multi Homepaes Demo</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">You can select multiple hompaes demo match demand</p>\n<a href="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature04.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2223" alt="Feature04" src="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature04.jpg" width="970" height="500" /></a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="features-big">\n<div class="container features-content">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">The Header that has it all.</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Customisable header with full social, shop, subscription, login &amp; language integration</p>\n<a href="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature05.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2225" alt="Feature05" src="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature05.jpg" width="980" height="590" /></a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="features-big">\n<div class="container features-content">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Unlimited Colors</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Unparalleled access to color properties, a total of 56 different elements that can be customised.</p>\n<a href="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature06.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2226" alt="Feature06" src="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature06.jpg" width="950" height="620" /></a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="features-big">\n<div class="container features-content">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Fontello icons.</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">361 web-related icons designed for use with Twitter Bootstrap. Infinitely scalable and Retina-ready.</p>\nOur Theme uses 4 sizes of icon (link-sized, small, medium &amp; large.) You can also have then contained, coloured and\naligned to your liking.\n\n<a href="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature07.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2227" alt="Feature07" src="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature07.jpg" width="900" height="201" /></a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="features-big">\n<div class="container features-content">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Fully Responsive &amp; Compatible with all browsers.</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">361 web-related icons designed for use with Twitter Bootstrap. Infinitely scalable and Retina-ready.</p>\nNeighborhood uses 4 sizes of icon (link-sized, small, medium &amp; large.) You can also have then contained, coloured and aligned to your liking.\n\n<a href="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature08.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2228" alt="Feature08" src="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature08.jpg" width="950" height="500" /></a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="features-big">\n<div class="features-content">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Revolutions Slider.</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Create a responsive(mobile friendly) or fullwidth slider with must-see-effects and meanwhile keep or build your SEO optimization (all content always readable for search engines).\nSee the heaps of custom transitions/animations for each object on the page! Customize this slider with our convenient drag&amp;drop backend to your very needs.This plugin features\ntons of unique transition effects, an image preloader, video embedding, autoplay that stops on user interaction and lots of easy to set options to create your own effects.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature09.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2229" alt="Feature09" src="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature09.jpg" width="1920" height="630" /></a></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="features-big">\n<div class="container features-content">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Advanced Grid System</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;">You will definitely like the way your product page like. You may set quanity of columms form 1 to 6</p>\n<a href="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature10.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2230" alt="Feature10" src="http://192.168.1.5/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Feature10.jpg" width="950" height="660" /></a>\n\n</div>\n</div>', 'Features', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'features', '', '', '2013-02-20 09:47:13', '2013-02-20 09:47:13', '', 0, 'http://apple.nova/wp/shaper_helix_ii_quickstart_wp/?page_id=53', 0, 'page', '', 0);
