(1946, 1, '2013-08-02 03:31:43', '2013-08-02 03:31:43', '<div class="homev4-big">\r\n<div class="container">[row class="homev4-content2"]\r\n[col class="span5"]\r\n<h2>Who is behind Femme Fatale Lashes?</h2>\r\nAs CEO of Femme Fatale Media Group, an award winning event staffing and model management agency, i''m constantly surrounded by the latest beauty products. I see what top models are using for runway, photo shoots and high profile events. When I came across mink lashes I immediately fell in love! What''s not to love? They transform your eyes into something amazing that no other lashes can! I wanted everyone to experience the beauty that came along with these, the only problem was the price and the quality I was finding.\r\n\r\nThat''s when my team set out to develop Femme Fatale Lashes. They''re made from the highest quality, 100% mink fur. They''re completely cruelty free, handmade, sterilized/hypo-allergenic and can be used up to 25 times! They immediately became a favorite of our models and celebrities alike, and so we decided to offer it to everyone! Offering the highest quality available, at the best price.\r\n\r\nYou too can live a model life.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n\r\nEmily Lyons\r\n\r\nFounder Femme Fatale Lashes\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n[col class="span7"]\r\n<img class="left" alt="" src="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/rsz_1emily-corporate-high_res.jpg" border="0" />\r\n[/col]\r\n[/row]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="homev4-big">\r\n<div class="container">[row class="homev4-content2"]\r\n[col class="span5"]\r\n<img alt="" src="http://novademo.com/wp_bearstore/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/example2.jpg" border="0" />\r\n[/col]\r\n[col class="span7"]\r\n<h2>Fully Responsive</h2>\r\nLorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry''s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It ha