(2407, 1, '2014-02-24 17:03:22', '2014-02-24 17:03:22', 'As CEO of Femme Fatale Media Group, an award winning event staffing and model management agency, i''m constantly surrounded by the latest beauty products. I see what top models are using for runway, photo shoots and high profile events. When I came across mink lashes I immediately fell in love! What''s not to love? They transform your eyes into something amazing that no other lashes can! I wanted everyone to experience the beauty that came along with these, the only problem was the price and the quality I was finding.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThat''s when my team set out to develop Femme Fatale Lashes. They''re made from the highest quality, 100% mink fur. They''re completely cruelty free, handmade, sterilized/hypo-allergenic and can be used up to 25 times! They immediately became a favorite of our models and celebrities alike, and so we decided to offer it to everyone! <b>Offering the highest quality available, at the best price. </b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nYou too can live a model life.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n\r\nEmily Lyons\r\n\r\nFounder Femme Fatale Lashes', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-24 17:03:22', '2014-02-24 17:03:22', '', 2, 'http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/uncategorized/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
