(2687, 1, '2014-03-21 00:03:32', '2014-03-21 00:03:32', '\r\n<img class="aligncenter" alt="" src="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/emilyteam.jpg" />\r\n<div class="homev4-big">\r\n<div class="container">[row class="homev4-content2"]\r\n[col class="span6"]\r\n<h2>Who Is Behind Femme Fatale Lashes?</h2>\r\n<span style="font-family: ''Caviar dreams'';">As CEO of Femme Fatale Media Group, an award winning event staffing and model management agency, i''m constantly surrounded by the latest beauty products. I see what top models are using for runway, photo shoots and high profile events. When I came across mink lashes I immediately fell in love! What''s not to love? They transform your eyes into something amazing that no other lashes can! I wanted everyone to experience the beauty that came along with these, the only problem was the price and the quality I was finding.That''s when my team set out to develop Femme Fatale Lashes.</span>\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n[col class="span6"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Why Femme Fatale Mink Lashes?</h2>\r\n[block type="rounded" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: ''Caviar dreams'';">They''re made from the highest quality, 100% mink fur.<BR>\r\nThey''re completely cruelty free, handmade, sterilized/hypo-allergenic and can be used up to 25 times!<BR>\r\nThey immediately became a favourite of our models and celebrities alike, and so we decided to offer it to everyone!<BR>\r\nOffering the highest quality available, at the best price.\r\n[/block][/col][/row]\r\n\r\n<div class="big-quote"><i><font face="caviar dreams">You too can live a model life!</i><BR><BR>Sincerely,\r\n<img alt="" src="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/signature.jpg" />\r\nEmily Lyons<BR>\r\nFounder Femme Fatale Lashes\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Home V4', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1946-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-21 00:03:32', '2014-03-21