(2715, 1, '2014-03-16 19:25:46', '2014-03-16 19:25:46', 'St Patricks Day, Femme Fatale style!\r\n\r\n1. The High Fashion Leprechaun\r\n<a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/maryna-linchuk-by-alexi-lubomirski-for-allure-august-2012-green-makeup-look.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2716" alt="Mink Lashes" src="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/maryna-linchuk-by-alexi-lubomirski-for-allure-august-2012-green-makeup-look-223x300.jpg" width="223" height="300" /></a>\r\n\r\nGet this look by taking a bright green shadow and completely lining your eye, blending it upwards to a cat eye. Pair it with a simple nude lipstick and bright green nails. Finish the look with our mink lashes in <a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/product/short-n-sweet/">Short N Sweet!</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n2. I Love Gold!\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/breath-g.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2717" alt="breath (g)" src="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/breath-g-300x190.jpg" width="300" height="190" /></a>\r\n\r\nYou will need bright yellow, light green, brown and black shadows to complete this look. Pairing it with a bright pink blush and lips to match. Finish the look with our stunning <a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/product/classic/">Classic</a> style mink lashes!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n3. Guiness Girl\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/green-eyes_3-jpg.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2718" alt="green-eyes_3-jpg" src="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/green-eyes_3-jpg-212x300.jpg" width="212" height="300" /></a>\r\n\r\nFor a more wearble look take a green shadow and line your eye, blending the colour up and through your crease. Take a white shadow to the inside corners. Finish it by filling in your brows, a light pink blush, lips and our <a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/product/au-natural/">Au Natural</a> mink lashes.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n4. Pot Of Green Gold\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/hawley-nail-laquers-yellow-pink.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2719" alt="mink lashes" src="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/hawley-nail-laquers-yellow-pink-300x187.jpg" width="300" height="187" /></a>\r\n\r\nFeeling a little more adventurous? Pair a bright lip with bright green and yellow eyes, black winged lines and mismatched nails! Finish it off with our <a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/product/carrie/">Carrie</a> mink lashes.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n5. Pretty Pattys Selfies\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/71974cde620a73cce3b3de42bef714cf.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2720" alt="mink lashes" src="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/71974cde620a73cce3b3de42bef714cf-300x300.jpg" width="300" height="300" /></a>\r\n\r\nA deep dark green mixed with a smokey black eye, bronzed skin and a pale lip will have you serious selfie-ing the night away! Of course the look wouldn''t be complete without a pair of <a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/product/femme-fatales/">Femme Fatale</a> mink lashes!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'St Patricks Day Makeup!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'st-patricks-day-makeup', '', '', '2014-03-16 19:26:48', '2014-03-16 19:26:48', '', 0, 'http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/?p=2715', 0, 'post', '', 0),
