(2758, 1, '2014-03-21 00:44:07', '2014-03-21 00:44:07', '<p></p>You want to keep your mink lashes in great condition so you can get the maximum use out of them. Use great care when applying and removing them. For best results apply your lashes after all your makeup has been applied.\r\n<p></P>\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="01" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams">Gently remove lashes from the packaging and measure them up against your eye. If needed trim from the outside corners so they fit just shorter then the natural length of your eye. [/blocknumber]\r\n\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="02" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams">Squeeze a bit of lash glue out onto a clean surface (we love Duo Eye-lash adhesive in clear-white. You can purchase it at Mac Cosmetics).[/blocknumber]\r\n\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="03" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams">Apply a thin layer of glue to the seam of the lashes. Wait a moment for the glue to become a little tacky.[/blocknumber]\r\n\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="04" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams"> Drop the lashes from above as close to your lash line as possible. Use tweezers to adjust them if necessary. Then give them a moment to dry.[/blocknumber]\r\n\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="05" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams">Once both are applied you can gently apply a liquid black liner over your upper lashlines to conceal the seems of the lash strips.[/blocknumber]\r\n\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="06" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams">Be sure to very gently remove glue and any makeup after each use.[/blocknumber]</font face>', 'How To Apply ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2566-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-21 00:44:07', '2014-03-21 00:44:07', '', 2566, 'http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/uncategorized/2566-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2759, 1, '2014-03-21 00:47:11', '2014-03-21 00:47:11', '[block type="rounded" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<center><font face="caviar dreams">We’d love to hear from you! Please fill out the attached form or email us at <a href="mailto:info@femmefatalemedia.com">info@femmefatalelashes.com</a><BR> and allow 24 hours for a reply.\r\n<p></P>Ask us about MUA & Friends and Family discounts!\r\n[/block]\r\n', 'Contact page', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '43-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-21 00:47:11', '2014-03-21 00:47:11', '', 43, 'http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/uncategorized/43-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
