(2782, 1, '2014-03-21 13:02:15', '2014-03-21 13:02:15', '<p></p><font face="caviar dreams">You want to keep your mink lashes in great condition so you can get the maximum use out of them. Use great care when applying and removing them. For best results apply your lashes after all your makeup has been applied.</font>\r\n<p></P>\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="01" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams">Gently remove lashes from the packaging and measure them up against your eye. If needed trim from the outside corners so they fit just shorter then the natural length of your eye. [/blocknumber]\r\n\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="02" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams">Squeeze a bit of lash glue out onto a clean surface (we love Duo Eye-lash adhesive in clear-white. You can purchase it at Mac Cosmetics).[/blocknumber]\r\n\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="03" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams">Apply a thin layer of glue to the seam of the lashes. Wait a moment for the glue to become a little tacky.[/blocknumber]\r\n\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="04" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams"> Drop the lashes from above as close to your lash line as possible. Use tweezers to adjust them if necessary. Then give them a moment to dry.[/blocknumber]\r\n\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="05" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams">Once both are applied you can gently apply a liquid black liner over your upper lashlines to conceal the seems of the lash strips.[/blocknumber]\r\n\r\n[blocknumber type="circle" text="06" color="#FFF" background="#ff5dba"]<font size="3" face="caviar dreams">Be sure to very gently remove glue and any makeup after each use.[/blocknumber]</font face>', 'How To Apply ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2566-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-21 13:02:15', '2014-03-21 13:02:15', '', 2566, 'http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/uncategorized/2566-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2788, 1, '2014-03-29 00:14:11', '2014-03-29 04:14:11', '<img src="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/emilyteam.jpg" align="center" border="3" bordercolor="#565656"/>\r\n<div class="homev4-big">\r\n<div class="container">[row class="homev4-content2"]\r\n[col class="span6"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Who Is Behind Femme Fatale Lashes?</h2>\r\n<h6>As CEO of Femme Fatale Media Group, an award winning event staffing and model management agency, i''m constantly surrounded by the latest beauty products. I see what top models are using for runway, photo shoots and high profile events. When I came across mink lashes I immediately fell in love! What''s not to love? They transform your eyes into something amazing that no other lashes can! I wanted everyone to experience the beauty that came along with these, the only problem was the price and the quality I was finding.That''s when my team set out to develop Femme Fatale Lashes.</h6>\r\n[/col]\r\n[col class="span6"]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Why Femme Fatale Mink Lashes?</h2>[block color="#FFFFFF" background="#ce4d9c"]\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">• They''re made from the highest quality, 100% mink fur.\r\n\r\n• They''re completely cruelty free, handmade, sterilized/hypo-allergenic and can be used up to 25 times!\r\n\r\n• They immediately became a favourite of our models and celebrities alike, and so we decided to offer it to everyone!\r\n\r\n• Offering the highest quality available, at the best price.[/block][/col][/row]</p><center><h3>Be prepared to break some hearts!</h3>Sincerely,\r\n<img alt="" src="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/em_black-10.png" />\r\nEmily Lyons\r\nFounder Femme Fatale Lashes', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-29 00:14:11', '2014-03-29 04:14:11', '', 2, 'http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/uncategorized/2-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
