(3005, 1, '2014-04-15 15:34:44', '2014-04-15 19:34:44', '<b>The Perfect Fit:</b></span></span></span>\r\n\r\nBefore you apply a new pair of Femme Fatale''s <a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com">Mink Lashes</a> you want to make sure you have the perfect fit. Ideally you want the lashes to be slightly shorter than the width of your eye. If necessary, trim your <strong>mink lashes</strong> to your desired size. Make sure you cut off very small increments until you reach your desired size so you don''t over-trim.</span></span></span>\r\n\r\n<b>Tools:</b></span></span></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>lash glue</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li>application stick (optional)</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li>tweezers (optional)</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe recommend “Duo Eye-lash adhesive” in clear-white. If you''re using an application stick, the end of an eye makeup brush will work best.</span></span></span>\r\n\r\n<b>Application:</span></span></span></b>\r\n\r\nWe prefer not to apply the glue directly on to the lashes. Squeeze a little glue onto a clean surface and using the end of the makeup brush as an applicator, dip it into the the glue. Using the applicator, paint a thin layer of glue along the seam of the lash. After you paint on the glue allow a few quick moments for the glue to partially dry. When the glue has become tacky, drop the lashes as close to your lash line as possible. Use tweezers to adjust the lashes to your liking. Once they are in place do not touch them until they have dried. Then to complete the look, we like to use liquid eyeliner to conceal any seams of the lash strips.</span></span></span>\r\n\r\n<b>Tips:</span></span></span></b>\r\n\r\nWhen your are letting the glue get a little tacky before applying, we like to wiggle the ends of the lashes back and forth to help form a curved shape.</span></span></span>\r\n\r\n<b>Maintenance:</span></span></span></b>\r\n\r\nFemme Fatale Lashes are very high quality. In order to optimize the life your lashes, make sure you always gently remove makeup and glue from them after use, and always store them in their case.</span></span></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'The Perfect Fit: How To Apply Our Lashes ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-apply-mink-lashes', '', '', '2014-04-15 15:44:44', '2014-04-15 19:44:44', '', 0, 'http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/?p=3005', 0, 'post', '', 0),
