(3023, 1, '2014-04-21 12:32:35', '2014-04-21 16:32:35', 'Hello, Gorgeous! It''s your big day and you deserve to go a little crazy. These are things our Femme Fatale models use on a regular basis to keep themselves looking gorgeous, we think they''re a must have for wedding day glam!\n\n1. Hydra Facial - Hydra facials leave your skin glowing and picture perfect ready. We recommend checking our <a href="http://www.beautybarlaserclinic.com">Beauty Bar Toronto</a> for yours!\n\n2. Mink Lashes - Um, OBVIOUSLY! We recommend a more natural looking lash like "<a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/product/classic/">The Classics</a>" or a touch more glamour with "The <a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/product/carrie/">Carrie''s</a>" or "<a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/product/barbie-girl-2/">Barbie Girl</a>." For really luxe we''d recommend going with the swarvoski crystal adorned "A Girl''s Best Friend."\n\n3. Lash tint - Lets face it, you''re probably going to cry. Aside from water proof mascara a lash tint is a must. It also has you beach ready should you be heading there for the honey moon!\n\n4. Hair treatment - We love keratine treatments! They leave your hair AH-MAZE-ING!\n\n5. Clip ins - Add volume or length with clip in extentions. There is no need paying a fortune for a pair, find a beauty outlet and sew on your own clips.\n\n6. Spray tan - Look for somewhere that offers natural ingredients so you aren''t coating your entire body in straight chemicals. We''d also recommend trying it months in advance so you know how it looks on you ahead of time.\n\n7. Mani/pedi with shellac - No chip, no fuss.\n\n8. Teeth whitening - Shine bright with pearly whites. We''ve been loving oil pulling, it''s cheap and natural. To learn more about it click <a href="http://www.youngandraw.com/oil-pulling-to-naturally-whiten-teeth-reduce-inflammation-and-detoxify-the-body/">here</a>.\n\n9. Shapewear - Hide any jiggly bits!\n\n10. Visine - You''re probably going to be tired and your eyes might get bloodshot, keeping visine on hand is a must!\n\nWhatever you decide to go with we''re sure you will look gorgeous!\n\nxo', 'Bridal Beauty Secrets ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3016-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-04-21 12:32:35', '2014-04-21 16:32:35', '', 3016, 'http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/uncategorized/3016-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3024, 1, '2014-04-21 14:44:11', '2014-04-21 18:44:11', 'Hello, Gorgeous! It''s your big day and you deserve to go a little crazy. Here are some things our Femme Fatale models use on a regular basis to keep themselves looking gorgeous, and we thought we share when with you because they are a must-have for Wedding Day Glam!\r\n\r\n1. Hydra Facial - Hydra facials leave your skin glowing and picture perfect ready. We recommend checking our <a href="http://www.beautybarlaserclinic.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #1155cc;">Beauty Bar Toronto</span></a> for yours!\r\n\r\n2. Mink Lashes - Um, OBVIOUSLY! We recommend a more natural looking lash like, "<span style="color: #1155cc;"><a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/product/classic/" target="_blank">Classic</a>”</span> or a touch more glamour with, "<span style="color: #1155cc;"><a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/product/carrie/" target="_blank">Carrie</a>,</span>" or, "<a href="http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/product/barbie-girl-2/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #1155cc;">Barbie Girl</span></a>." For a really luxe look, we''d recommend going with the Swarovski crystal adorned, "A Girl''s Best Friend."\r\n\r\n3. Lash Tinting - Lets face it, you''re probably going to cry. Keep the look of mascara, minus the ink running down your face with this semi-permanent treatment. And it''s also perfect for when you''re spending your days on the beach (hint hint: honeymoon!)\r\n\r\n4. Hair Treatments - We love Keratin treatments! They leave your hair soft and silky. You will not regret it!\r\n\r\n5. Clip-ins - Add volume or length to your hair with clip-in extensions. There is no need paying a fortune for a pair, we recommend getting a pair from a beauty outlet and sewing them onto hairclips yourself!\r\n\r\n6. Spray Tan - When done right spray tans make you look sun-kissed and beautiful. We recommend trying it months in advance so you can preview the result.\r\n\r\n7. Mani/pedi with shellac - No chip, no fuss. Will last all honeymoon!\r\n\r\n8. Teeth Whitening - Nothing beats a bright and shiny smile! We''ve been loving oil pulling, it''s cheap and natural. To learn more about it click <a href="http://www.youngandraw.com/oil-pulling-to-naturally-whiten-teeth-reduce-inflammation-and-detoxify-the-body/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #1155cc;">here</span></a>.\r\n\r\n9. Shapewear - Look svelte in that white dress with some Spanx. They are a girls best friend\r\n\r\n10. Visine - You don''t want to look tired or red-eyed in your photos. A few drops of Visine keeps your eyes clear and beautiful.\r\n\r\nAnd no matter what tips you decide to go with, remember confidence goes a long way. Enjoy your day because it''s all about you!\r\n\r\nxo\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Bridal Beauty Secrets ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3016-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-21 14:44:11', '2014-04-21 18:44:11', '', 3016, 'http://www.femmefatalelashes.com/uncategorized/3016-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
